    - target: {fileID: 5473530577572799402, guid: fc2cfbe3e37b7814ea4002360a9f2723, type: 3}
      propertyPath: Text
      value: Took you long enough, kid. Welcome to <color="blue">Major</color> <color="blue">Mountains</color>,
        a place of peace, harmony, and musicality. ; When news spread of a <color="red">music</color>
        <color="red">thief</color> scraping the web, these folks quickly took their
        music down and backed it up on a <color="blue">disc</color>. ; Long story
        short - he's taking the <color="blue">disc</color> for himself, poaching
        resources and destroying instruments along the way. ; You'll need to harvest
        the power of rhythm to beat him! I've just connected to your headset-I'll
        share tips as you go.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
